Every Heartfelt Thing Prince Harry Has Said About the Royal Baby During Australian Tour|http://www.elle.com/culture|http://www.elle.com/culture/a23981313/prince-harry-public-comments-royal-baby/||2018-10-20|Ariana Yaptangco||Prince Harry is a very proud dad-to-be! Since Kensington Palace announced that Meghan Markle is expecting her first child, the royal has said the most heartfelt things about Meghan and the royal baby while on Australian tour.

Earlier this week, Harry appeared on Good Morning America and excitedly thanked a room full of Aussie officials for their support and well-wishes. &quot;Thank you for the incredibly warm welcome and the chance to meet so many Aussies from all walks of life...we also genuinely couldn&#39;t think of a better place to announce the...upcoming baby, whether it be a boy or a girl,&quot; he said. &quot;So thank you very, very much.&quot; Meghan was also shown smiling and applauding.

